<br />

<br />
I worked hard and played a lot, I'm almost 57 now but it's only because I found a good semi-regular group to play with. Make friends, if your guild has a website start posting for a regular get together, find some people you work well with and keep them together, take them to different places and kill stuff. 
<br />
With a lot of work and a good group it's not as bad as you think. 
