				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: lvl 55-60 <a name="34356"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 13 04 8:08 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Best xp I've found for late 50's is Droga. Was in king room last night and xp there made tier 1 POP xp look bad. Group was 59 war, 65 sham, 55 cleric, 55 paladiin, and 57 bard (me). We owned that room and were all freak'n out over the xp. The hardest part is the break in since you can not mez any of them and you better have good dps if you want to break in from the outside because respawn is pretty fast. If you break room from the inside, you will have at least two mobs if you fight on just one side where there are two spawns, just don't let them run and keep them in the wall. Mobs were all 59-61. Just make sure you play resists with the casters, Very Important. The cleric said he was rarely having to heal, his mana was almost always 80%+. Have shaman ready with root as they love to resist your snare. I would twist only one other song besides snare once mob got down to 20% to make sure i could get 3 snare attempts in if needed. Having two tanks is a must IMO because you will have two at a time occationally. Plus, if you are lucky and get a hammer or two, thats some real nice plat<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />) We were there to get a hammer for the warrior.
<br />

<br />
Mal</span></td>
